The,Mozilla,Web,Activities,API,allows,an,application,to,delegate,the,performance,of,tasks,such,as,image,selection,or,email,forwarding,to,another,application,chosen,by,the,user,Developers,use,the,API,to,provide,interfaces,for,implementing,seamless,transfer,of,tasks,from,the,app,that,delegates,an,activity,to,the,one,that,handles,the,task,The,API,is,currently,compatible,with,only,Firefox,OS